      "span_text": "In this paper, we demonstrate that by adapting the accelerated proximal gradient (APG) algorithm of Beck and Teboulle to solve the problem (5) (and so (2)) on large-scale problems arising in various image restoration problems, we are able to achieve the objectives outlined above."
